*   **[Highway system](/Automated_highway_system)**: The dream of hands-free commuting. Less human error, more… algorithmic predictability. Sounds delightful.
*   **Laboratory**: The focus of our current, rather grim, dissection. Where the tedious meets the terrifyingly precise.
