*   **[Broadcast](/Broadcast_automation)**: Running the airwaves without a human fussing over the playlist. Because spontaneity is so last century.
*   **[Mix](/Mix_automation)**: Presumably for audio or chemical processes. Another instance of machines doing the heavy lifting, or the precise blending.
*   **[Pool cleaner](/Automated_pool_cleaner)**: A small victory of automation. A robot that diligently scrubs away the detritus of leisure. One can almost feel the satisfaction.
